Da, juđ. Blizu mora.

01:11:06.047 --> 01:11:07.829
A to! "Jug".

01:11:08.221 --> 01:11:09.569
Pa to sam i rekao.

01:11:11.570 --> 01:11:12.569
"Juđ"!

01:11:13.440 --> 01:11:14.439
Dobra.

01:11:15.484 --> 01:11:16.745
"Dobra."

01:11:18.397 --> 01:11:19.615
Zajebava me.

01:11:23.399 --> 01:11:24.443
Zajebava me.

01:11:25.400 --> 01:11:27.356
Samo jedan WC za 300 ljudi.

